CreateTemplateFile
- ask user "Give me a description of the template you need for %fileName%", write to %user%
- call goal ProcessAnswer continue=false

ProcessAnswer
- read file llm/CreateTemplateFileSystem.llm, load vars, write to %system%
- [llm] system: %system%
        user: %user%
        model: 'gpt-4o'
        continue prev: %continue%
        scheme: {ask:string|null, templateContent:string}
        write to %result%
- if %result.ask% is not empty then call AskUser ask=%result.ask%, else SaveTemplate

AskUser
- ask user %ask%, write to %user%
- call goal ProcessAnswer continue=true

SaveTemplate
- save %result.templateContent% to %goal.AbsoluteGoalFolderPath%/%fileName%